    <text id="B0405T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>McDonnell asks Waldo to recommend loyal and qualified men for the posts of
                    Commonwealth's Attorney and County Clerk</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <head>
                    Bureau <abbr expan="Refugees, Freedmen and Abandoned Lands">R. F. &amp; A.
                        L.</abbr><lb/>Head <abbr expan="Quarters">Qrs.</abbr> 9th Sub <abbr
                            expan="District">Dist.</abbr>
                    <abbr expan="Virginia">Va.</abbr>
                    <name type="recipient">Roswell Waldo<lb/><abbr
                            expan="Assistant Sub Assistant Commissioner"
                        >A.S.A.Comr</abbr><lb/>Staunton, <abbr expan="Virginia">Va.</abbr></name>
                </head>

                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1868-12-07"><abbr expan="December">Dec</abbr> 7th 1868</date>
                        <name type="place">Winchester</name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Sir</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>You will please recommend such persons to be men who have been loyal to the
                    Government <unclear>provided</unclear> such can be found who have the necessary
                    qualifications for Commonwealth Attorney and County Clerk in each County in your
                    Division, as would be willing to serve and are qualified for the position.</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>Very Respectfully<lb/>Your <abbr expan="Obedient Servant">Obedt
                        St</abbr></salute>
                    <signed>John A. McDonnell<lb/>Sub <abbr expan="Assistant Commissioner">Asst
                        Comr</abbr></signed>
                    <seg type="postscript">Please give political status</seg>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
